							<h1 class="articleTitle">Union Pub Announces 9/4 Chicago Bears Kickoff Celebration</h1>
							<p class="date">8/24/11</p>
							<p>On Sunday, September 4, the Union Pub will be hosting the "DC Bears 2011 Kickoff Celebration", which is a DC Chicago Bears fan reunion and pep rally. The day's festivities will start after brunch (3pm), and last into the evening. Festivities include:</p>
							<ul>
								<li>Game Day atmosphere, including 2011 Bears food and drink specials, fight songs, and game day decor.</li>
								<li>Classic Chi-Bears games and "History of the Bears" films on the big screens and HD screens throughout the restaurant.</li>
								<li>Raffle - prizes include gift certificates, Bears memorabilia, and two GRAND PRIZEs - a Union Pub "Season Ticket" (one table for two, reserved in the winners name for every 2011 Chicago Bears football game) and a pair of tickets to Soldier Field for a 2011 Bears game (date TBD).</li>
